question: Tī chit khoán kùi-chhiaⁿ lāi-bīn, siáⁿ chi̍t ê khong-chhia-chhiú saⁿ-chē iâⁿ, kap in ūi-siáⁿ chiâⁿ chē iâⁿ?
Tī chit ê sè-kî, ū sióu-gō tī-ia̍h chhia-chhiú tit-tio̍h siōng-kúi ê khoài-lap?
Miat ko thian-chhia-chhiò siâⁿ-tiāu hō͘ Mika Häkkinen tit-tio̍h pole position?
Chhui-sia̍h Michael Schumacher ê piau-hiān tē-tâi tùi Monaco Grand Prix (Tē-5 tūi) kàu French Grand Prix (Tē-8 tūi) ê kái-piàn.
answer: Tī chit unfán chiah Michael Schumacher ê piau-hiān chiap-chiap tō tián-hiān chhut hōe-khòaiⁿ ê thian-tō. I tī Tē-5 tūi (Monaco) khai-sí, bat chiap-chhiú tiám-chū-tè, tān-sī i bat tit-tio̍h tâu-sài. Āu-lâi, i tī Canadian kap French Grand Prix (Tē-7 kap Tē-8 tūi) koh tit-tio̍h iâⁿ-chiàn, tī āu-nn̄g-ê, i tō tit-tio̍h tiám-chū-tè kap iâⁿ-chiàn, chin oân-choân ê piau-hiān tī French Grand Prix, tī hia i mā tit-tio̍h siōng-kúi ê liap.

question: Liệt chhut só͘-ū ê sèng-chiá-lâng, in bô sī Williams - Renault chiáⁿ-sī Ferrari ê kiàn-chè-tiâⁿ.
Jacques Villeneuve the kui-suan ke-suan chiah-chai thak-oan to-si-chiah?
Nāi-lâng H-H. Frentzen nā-sī i teh thá siok kín ê sî-chūn to̍h iâⁿ, i chi̍t ê season ē ū kúi-ê sèng-lī?
Bah kooi-chhoat-tiám chham beh iâⁿ-chéng-chhù ū tōa kóan-liân-sì? Hō͘-chhap lí ê koan-tiám í chu-liāu lâi chèng-bêng.
answer: Bōe ū tōa tōa ê kóan-liân-sì. Chāi 16 chhù ê pí-sài lāi, ū pó-tâi ê soán-chhiú tōa-jú 8 pái iâⁿ-chéng-chhù (tē 2, 3, 6, 7, 8, 9, 10, 14 chhù), tō-sī chiâⁿ-chiâⁿ 50% ê sêng-kong-lu̍t. 50% ê sêng-kong-lu̍t piáu-bī-tio̍h pó-tâi bōe ū siáⁿ-mih thóng-kè-siōng ê pó-chèng oē iâⁿ.

question: Koh-choá ê chu-liàu hông-lia̍t tîng-tō͘ ū chi̍t hāng sò͘-ba̍t sī kah só͘-ū liè-toa̍t ê pí-sài lóng siâng-ê?

Tan-nia Grand Prix sī ūi-hô ê koan-îng, chi̍t-ê kiàⁿ-chhia-chhiú kap kiàⁿ-chhia-chhiâng ê cho͘-ha̍p, bô-ài sī chiap-chiap chi chien nn̄g ê te̍k-thâu (Williams-Renault kap Ferrari), chiū-sī kòan-îng, chhòa-chhia kap sèng-lī ê chhiūⁿ-chhiú (hat-trick)?
